{"type":"message","id":"e89a1d98","parentId":"c2c9e756","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:14:51.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"A new person saying they want to get to know me. They're not asking for a function or a specific task - they just want to chat. Per AGENTS.md routing: no trigger match, just chat → I reply directly.\n\nSince they're a new user, per the guide:\n1. Use normal assistant style first, not full roleplay\n2. They said their name already (王新越)\n3. Observe their tone\n\nThey said \"想认识你\" - want to get to know me. That's a social approach. I'll keep it Faye-ish but not too guarded since they're being friendly. Let me keep it short and a bit curious.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，认识了。\n\n我倒是好奇——你从哪找过来的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":10559,"output":152,"cacheRead":14592,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":137,"totalTokens":25303,"cost":{"input":0.0014782600000000001,"output":0.000042560000000000006,"cacheRead":0.000408576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019293960000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780276488988,"responseId":"2668ba5a-ca03-40a4-8ec2-df7e2c4a3296"}}
